earch)&lt;br&gt;   86k lives-eq/$1k · 58% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up The Humane League · 22%&lt;br&gt;(Sam Peltzman, Luisa Rodriguez)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + suffering_focused + resilience_undermines_deterrence&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Peltzman effect for civil defence: making nuclear war survivable weakens deterrence and raises the chance of war, so a resilient-food dollar partly insures against a catastrophe it also makes marginally likelier. An alternative, lower estimate for ALLFED, anchored to Rodriguez&#x27;s ~0.4%/yr US-Russia war probability. Requires future people to be in the circle. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtz2zYW%2FSt3PNtdKSvRpN6y151xYrnN1HYztrOdTpxRIBKSsKFILgBaUdL0t%2FcAJCXKpiZK9UVDkcC55z5xL74cBXzK0lC%2FigN%2BdHJ0fExnZ2d0L5mISMfkS%2FZ5hYdlRA9py%2FU6tIxlGDwKvqSlN26Nu%2BPeeDD2PKopHSfkeXUD8BAB6FypdJFoEUfkz4F3Qi4lTMb%2BXLDQwHnDFnk0ZXLMlmw1nqcLFqniQ4tYJBYsVGMVL%2FhyznTxpUvTVKeS5xvGC6Y1l%2BOl0PNxIJQfp5EW0axY3qMoLr8fb%2B0uVg1IpdMpl3ZB7KeKB2uKHkmuRCh45PNxGgVcLkTE1TjgkCvNW6vviPlzYhulhSJGb1Z6juepCDnBpJvP6pi0UYoFgWpAAPxgQCmWFkzyJmzFFkaEUHiv5zwz478U9I98i3FKfrxIYmXUXS%2FAXsMRCui5UBZNaRYFLIwjTgs4OnTow9qPo8cPhqrZzj8l3NfY%2BMjClFM8tQgblzsW7CVXmibpiqwpzEbFy4qd0PlrUmzK9YpqtzxYxnFAt1jEpD%2BvZxg%2FjW5Gt%2Bf3owuarGjGIy6Z5k6yKqKMB0JvGesFPjbgSZ1RMvYEksV6CwdIbRRfxBKRtbabytZmRmFJAg8qh%2B5WCyeMZ1EsEV21L0m3Qcmw%2B7VusazPhu4P9Or1qV054ZplbxMZT9gEYaBBZBIb5QOTIu%2FcBnnvHbpkvo4hk8ksHAQWJMYTkW6Qiomb8IjlDP4bvVtenF%2F9fvyP9zThYbxEDpi91s%2F8E57DFbYDG7a1WJAdpL7OPAIfckQu1J%2BGcYpdc7j%2FIg9wOnuuIBLPcQdWTfM4%2BFonsiEGTOiw5GI2BzbSVHJmU2cOa5loVFS7jxdMiY%2Bn9F8oZL613JYLY63T5Y0UoA5fV0r2HC8X3HO6uWD%2BSUtWEsse4T8DDZ15hGBaY%2B8WnyVxSWvPQid42dRiwenf5DP