simulation + person_affecting_view&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence → 14 time_of_perils_exit → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WWtT20gW%2FSu3qJ1dm8FG8tuwTBUJZia1JEMB2ampkHLaUtvuQVJruyWMk0l%2B%2B55uSbaMReEMNV8oIXXfe%2B65z25%2F2fP5lKVB8lr6fO9o7%2FCQTk5O6EYxEVEiyVPs8xIPi4hu05bjdmghVeDfC76ghTtujbvj3ngwdt2x2xm7vbHbp5pOZExuv24k3UaQeKp1GsaJkBF5cwg%2BIodipqQ3Fywwct1hi1yaMjVmC7Ycz9OQRbr40CIWiZAFeqxlyBdzlhRfujRNk1TxfMM4ZEnC1XghkvnYF9qTaZSIaFYs71Eky%2B%2FHG7uLVQPS6XTKlV0gvVRzfwXRJcW1CASPPD5OI5%2BrUERcj30Ovcq8XS3tUCJCPpbTcQxZAM8fxAq426NA3BsNIhprEaYBs%2BwUn%2FuETVpGYwYknsVqGLdkjpg3J7ZmVGhidLlM5nieioATHLf%2BrA8pMYwx39cHQA9vG8QklRWmeAOOYKHBLzTeJ3Oe%2BehfGuRGnpVxTJ4MY6kNl6sF2GsIADvJXGgrTScs8lkgI04hwilo0qdVtIzuPxmoZjt%2FiGEUNt6zIOUkp1bCOrCaVtgrrhOapEuyPJuNmpcNO6IbyPrF%2BI7TBWezlGcbfx69G12d3ozOaLKkGY%2B4YglvxssigLkPR5QZ2sfHA8RGkuEwJEKSlfUeLlWJsTaUCrG6IktnazMmWBwjJnSTrpdhM5CzSCrEa%2B1L3D2geNj9WreyrKOGzg%2F0%2Bs2xXTnhCcvexkpO2ASBlQDIRBqLfZN9H5wDcj826Zx5iYROpngmCgtiQ3%2BUHJCWxE1MSDWD00YfFmenF78f%2FuMjTXggF8gqs9c6lz%2FgOVhiO2SDUCsLuv3USzI3wHEcuQDzp4FMsWsOn5%2FlKUMn2wYilZvOwJppHgdf60Q2riATNiy4mM0hG4mvOLPJOAdbJgQ11W5kyLS4O6b%2FwiDzreW0HJC1SsBLJQA9WVZrdpturrjX7OaK%2BUOiWEktu4f%2FjGjYzCNE0