ce + space_expansion_backfires&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The sweet-spot view: the capability that settles planets also moves asteroids and exports nationalism off-world (Deudney, Dark Skies), and genuinely decorrelated self-sufficient settlements are far further away than boosterism assumes (Weinersmiths, A City on Mars) — so below a large number of independent settlements, expansion ADDS anthropogenic risk, and accelerating it before geopolitics matures is net-negative. The perils window stays open far longer, the expected future shrinks, and x-risk work keeps its urgency but loses most of its astronomical multiplier. Mutually exclusive with the time-of-perils-exit reading. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence → 15 space_expansion_backfires" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWf1z2zYS%2FVd2PNc7KSfJpL5lnzvjxHKbOSfN2M51OnFGgUhIRM2vA0ArSpr%2B7fcAkhJlS2el%2BiWjkMDbtw%2B7i13665HPZywL9avE50cnR8fHdHZ2RreSiZh0Qp5kX5b4sYjpLms7bpcWiQz9B8EXtHAn7Ulv0p8MJ647cXtUUzpJye3VDcZdDKxzpbIo1SKJyQsAeUIOpUwmXiBYaBDdUZtcmjE5YQu2nARZxGJVvmgTi0XEQjVRScQXAdPlmx7NMp1JXmyYRExrLicLoYOJL5SXZLEW8bxc3qc4qT6fbOwuVw1JZbMZl3ZB4mWK%2ByuKLkmuRCh47PFJFvtcRiLmauJz2JXm6Wppj1TKsIp%2FTgEO1ydT5t3PBACsJmPmBcTWwghFjN4tdYDfMxFygvLr1%2BqYtHGc%2Bb5qgASOyximRFowyZvQk0WGhlB4rgOeS%2F0PBY1iz2KckpdEaaKMJKsF2Gv8gJM6EDk1pVnsszCJOUWIh7BFn1bHPX74ZKia7fCMexobH1iYcUpmFmEdGS0L9pIrTdNsSVYus1HxqmMndP6aFJtxvaTaNfcXSeLTNRYx6QX1HOOn8dvx9fnt%2BIKmS5rzmEumeStdlsHIfaE3xHqBlw2cts4pGT2BZLHe45CkNo5HiUT0rXRT%2BdpcFJamOGXVoptl1AqTeZxIRGDta9prUDrqfatbLHtmI%2BcHevX61K6ccs3yp6lMpmyKUNEgMk2M877JpA9Og9yPLbpknk5gk0meQ2FBak4i1g1SCXETHomc4%2FzGHxYX51e%2FHf%2FtI015mCyQJ2avPWf%2BGb%2FDJbYDG9paLNj2M0%2FnJ4Iz5AhAuD8Lkwy7Ahz%2FRZEEdPbUQSRnyxlaN83P4bc6kQ0xYMKHBRfzANhIZcmZTa8AaploVFS7TSKmxP0p%2FQcOmXdtp%2B1ArFVKvZMC1HHWWy27Lbcw3G%2F1CsP8s5asYpY94PwMNHzmMYJphb3bfJ7oFa9